Data

baseglm_df <- read_feather("../assets/clean_data/baseglm_df.feather")
baseglm_df
baseglm_df %>% 
  slice(2:15) %>% #Start with age groups only
  ggplot(aes(or, term)) +
  geom_vline(aes(xintercept = 1), 
             size = 0.25, 
             linetype = "dashed") +
  geom_errorbarh(aes(xmax = ci95_upper, xmin = ci95_lower), 
                size = 0.5,
                height = 0.2,
                colour = "black") +
  geom_point(size = 2, colour = "#4477AA") +
  labs(title = "Mortality odds ratio",
       subtitle = "Reference: age_grp19-24",
       y = "",
       x = "Odds ratio")

baseglm_df %>% 
  slice(17:25) %>% #loinc_decil
  ggplot(aes(or, term)) +
  geom_vline(aes(xintercept = 1), 
             size = 0.25, 
             linetype = "dashed") +
  geom_errorbarh(aes(xmax = ci95_upper, xmin = ci95_lower), 
                size = 0.5,
                height = 0.2,
                colour = "black") +
  geom_point(size = 2, colour = "#4477AA") +
  labs(title = "Mortality odds ratio",
       subtitle = "Reference: loinc_decile10",
       y = "",
       x = "Odds ratio")

baseglm_df %>% 
  slice(27:38) %>% #province
  ggplot(aes(or, term)) +
  geom_vline(aes(xintercept = 1), 
             size = 0.25, 
             linetype = "dashed") +
  geom_errorbarh(aes(xmax = ci95_upper, xmin = ci95_lower), 
                size = 0.5,
                height = 0.2,
                colour = "black") +

       subtitle = "Reference: provinceOntario",
       y = "",
       x = "Odds ratio")

baseglm_df %>% 
  slice(45:46) %>% #generation
  ggplot(aes(or, term)) +
  geom_vline(aes(xintercept = 1), 
             size = 0.25, 
             linetype = "dashed") +
  geom_errorbarh(aes(xmax = ci95_upper, xmin = ci95_lower),
